    <section style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Rationale (brief)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Clarity:</strong> Minimal elements per screen; labels for primary actions.</li>
        <li><strong>Hierarchy:</strong> Title &gt; primary CTA &gt; secondary actions; consistent spacing.</li>
        <li><strong>Consistency:</strong> Reused patterns for lists, buttons, and modals.</li>
        <li><strong>Feedback:</strong> States for loading, error, and success are sketched.</li>
      </ul>
